{"type": "article", "id": 45435, "title": "有个柴犬收纳盒，它总是坐在桌边｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-09-21T23:15:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 44237, "name": "PAIX Design"}, {"id": 32650, "name": "YOU+MORE！"}, {"id": 30796, "name": "Areaware"}, {"id": 44238, "name": "The Butcher’s Shop Design"}, {"id": 44239, "name": "Donald Corey"}, {"id": 44240, "name": "Todd McLellan"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 244, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170922071528N2s0xcyeijzTCL8O.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Fly Me to The Moon by 長門屋</h3><p>还记得那个<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/43286.html\">可以看到银河的羊羹</a>吗？在把羊羹做得更美这件事上，来自福岛县会津市的百年和菓子老铺<a href=\"http://shop.nagatoya.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">長門屋</a>进行了一次突破，将羊羹原本单一的横截面转变成了不断变化的故事书：在最新推出的 Fly Me to The Moon 羊羹一侧，是一只飞向三日月（意指新月）的蓝鸟。随着羊羹被一块块切下，你就能见证它不断展翅飞向满月的过程。这是它的<a href=\"http://shop.nagatoya.net/?pid=115061246#\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 3500 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190031rcSmMkqyWTb6F0GN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667123\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190031hyZ4Pb38YvViqwfH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668493\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190031dte16mJpNaHycV7i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667123\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190031KNbTrFEqmSdtGnIY.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.493151\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mexxenger by PAIX Design</h3><p>2015 年，一群热衷于智能产品的台湾设计师组成了一支名为 <a href=\"http://paixdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">PAIX Design</a> 的团队，致力于开发富有科技感的包具。继 2016 年推出智能背包 Backpaix 之后，他们最近又带来了智能邮差包 Mexxenger。邮差包的智能要素在于正面的 Smart Dock 接口以及团队开发的徽章，目前有手电、摄像头以及智能显示屏三款可选——只要在配套的 App 进行简单设置，徽章就可以变成一个用来交流的表情包。邮差包本身拥有超过 16 个收纳空间且采用防水内袋，它还配备了无线充电板，只要将手机滑入即可充电。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/paix/mexxenger-high-tech-modular-messenger-bag\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从 169 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211900415DkrozFAZO8yLNtX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190041WoKm3bpRSqvjl6FM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661765\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211900413UpmOKHJv5DqATy7.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.441176\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190041m4CqQixu8MjgyObE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190041pl61XGkRadziBsA2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190040pbqTctkw42vNsCzh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.856083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Shiba Inu Hanging Rack by YOU+MORE！</h3><p>一个人坐在饭桌前感到寂寞？总能把小动物变成治愈系家居产品的日本品牌 YOU+MORE！想到了一个深得犬系爱好者欢心的点子——这三只“端坐”在桌边的柴犬是旗下新开发的一款收纳产品，柴犬藏在桌面下的肚子其实是个 26 厘米深的抽屉，背部还有一个小口袋可以用来放置遥控器等杂物。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.felissimo.co.jp/youmore/wk57514/gcd493835/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 3132 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190104zGUWZ2O5J6fAa93q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190104JWA1sYCGlq0tN6dp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709211901050BAgQ3CfG6qjxc2o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190105ME5UWYQrG0kfZeSw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.816667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Plywood Playing Cards by Donald Corey</h3><p>用扑克牌搭东西的时候总是提心吊胆怕它倒下？不妨试试美国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.donaldcorey.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Donald Corey</a> 为设计品牌 <a href=\"https://www.areaware.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Areaware</a> 打造的这套木质扑克。它的牌面被设计得相当精简，被放大的花色中央印有白色的符号，四周围则留有 8 个插槽。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.areaware.com/collections/all/products/plywood-playing-cards?variant=17519980484\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 23 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190115Ty4VOUXIlpuas1rP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714444\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190115FJgsWbPajw0UdHRZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190115WczDt7ryYq4OeTiC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714355\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190115ZuLlzWMbXDykwHRh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Little Sumo by The Butcher’s Shop Design</h3><p>为了帮助客户的杜松子酒从各种偏向于嬉皮风的包装中脱颖而出，设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.thebutchersshop.co.za/\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Butcher’s Shop</a> 以日本相扑运动员那胖墩墩的身形为灵感，打造了一个名为 Little Sumo 的概念品牌。圆润的瓶身上只有相当简洁的标签，配上瓶颈处的相扑手头像，相当醒目。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190206SOBbt7j29pG54er6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190206GfYbZ14PdFcNqeug.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190206ics50tvHefOAqRzl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Things Come Apart by Todd McLellan</h3><p>小的时候有没有因为好奇心旺盛，经常把身边的物件给摆弄到解体？在美国艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.toddmclellan.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Todd McLellan</a> 眼中，这些拆解下来的部件有着独特的魅力，因此他从 2009 年起就一直在进行一项名为 Things Come Apart 的摄影创作，展现零件之美。他将它们收集到一块儿、工整地排列开来，在留下一张像是组装指南的俯拍照之后，他又会利用它们拍摄一张具有冲击力的“爆破”照片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190128PBT2AxN0VaFMvIG5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190127bOsKqjSlX8J1utNk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190127uGQ0y8onWlCis6qj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.300390\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170921190127LeWV6fQHUliZ0MJT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.331361\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}